PrecisAuthority to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Province of Ontario which provides for the establishment of the CANADA-ONTARIO BUSINESS SERVICE CENTRE in Toronto to support business development and entrepreneurial processes by providing a single telephone access point for accurate, speedy and user-friendly information or assistance on where to get further information on government programs and services.
Attachments
precis:
Authority to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Province of Ontario which
provides for the establishment of the CANADA-ONTARIO BUSINESS SERVICE
CENTRE in Toronto to support business development and entrepreneurial
processes by providing a single telephone access point for accurate,
speedy and user-friendly information or assistance on where to get
further information on government programs and services.
